      "text": [
        " امْرَأَةٍ مَجْنُونَةٍ زَنَتْ قَالَ إِنَّهَا لَا تَمْلِكُ أَمْرَهَا وَ لَيْسَ عَلَيْهَا شَيْ‏ءٌ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ali Bin Al Hakam, from Al A’ala Bin Razeyn, from Muhammad Bin Muslim, ",
          "(It has been narrated either) from one of the two (5<sup>th</sup> or 6<sup>th</sup> Imam<sup>asws</sup>) regarding an insane woman who committed adultery. He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘She had no control over her affair, and there is nothing upon her’."
        ]
